      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Flicker in the Night",
        "Client": "Dame Fiorayne",
        "Description": "Our last outing together was\r\na great experience for me.\r\nI hope we\u0027ll have more chances\r\nto hunt together! In fact, I\u0027m\r\nbeing dispatched to the Shrine\r\nRuins tonight to deal with a\r\nTobi-Kadachi. Care to join me?",
        "Target": "Hunt a Tobi-Kadachi",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Lueur nocturne",
        "Client": "Dame Fiorayne",
        "Description": "J\u0027ai ador\u00E9 chasser ensemble\r\nl\u0027autre fois. J\u0027esp\u00E8re que ce\r\nne sera pas la derni\u00E8re !\r\nMaintenant que j\u0027y pense, je\r\ndois chasser un Tobi-Kadachi\r\nau Temple oubli\u00E9, \u00E7a te tente\r\nde m\u0027accompagner ?",
        "Target": "Chasser un Tobi-Kadachi",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Scintillio nel buio",
        "Client": "Dama Fiorayne",
        "Description": "La nostra ultima caccia\r\ninsieme \u00E8 stata una magnifica\r\nesperienza. Spero che avremo\r\naltre occasioni. A proposito,\r\nstasera verr\u00F2 inviata alle\r\nRovine sacre per occuparmi di\r\nun Tobi-Kadachi. Vuoi venire?",
        "Target": "Caccia un Tobi-Kadachi",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Flackern in der Nacht",
        "Client": "Fiorayne",
        "Description": "Unser letzter gemeinsamer Aus-\r\nflug war eine tolle Erfahrung\r\nf\u00FCr mich. Heute Abend werde\r\nich zu den Heiligen Ruinen\r\ngeschickt, um mich einem\r\nTobi-Kadachi anzunehmen.\r\nMagst du dich mir anschlie\u00DFen?",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Tobi-Kadachi.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Centelleo nocturno",
        "Client": "Fiorayne",
        "Description": "Nuestra \u00FAltima cacer\u00EDa fue una\r\ngran experiencia. \u00A1Ojal\u00E1 pueda\r\nseguir cazando contigo! Es m\u00E1s,\r\nesta noche me han pedido que\r\nvaya al Templo olvidado para\r\nencargarme de un Tobi-Kadachi.\r\n\u00BFMe echar\u00EDas una mano?",
        "Target": "Caza un Tobi-Kadachi",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u0412\u0441\u043F\u044B\u0448\u043A\u0430 \u0432 \u043D\u043E\u0447\u0438",
        "Client": "\u0420\u044B\u0446\u0430\u0440\u044C \u0424\u0438\u043E\u0440\u0430\u0439\u043D\u0430",
        "Description": "\u041D\u0430\u0448\u0430 \u043F\u043E\u0441\u043B\u0435\u0434\u043D\u044F\u044F \u043E\u0445\u043E\u0442\u0430\r\n\u043E\u0431\u043E\u0433\u0430\u0442\u0438\u043B\u0430 \u043C\u0435\u043D\u044F \u043E\u043F\u044B\u0442\u043E\u043C.\r\n\u041D\u0430\u0434\u0435\u044E\u0441\u044C, \u043C\u044B \u0435\u0449\u0435 \u043D\u0435 \u0440\u0430\u0437 \u0441\u043C\u043E\u0436\u0435\u043C\r\n\u043F\u043E\u043E\u0445\u043E\u0442\u0438\u0442\u044C\u0441\u044F \u0432\u043C\u0435\u0441\u0442\u0435! \u041A\u0441\u0442\u0430\u0442\u0438,\r\n\u0441\u0435\u0433\u043E\u0434\u043D\u044F \u0432\u0435\u0447\u0435\u0440\u043E\u043C \u043C\u0435\u043D\u044F \u043F\u043E\u0441\u044B\u043B\u0430\u044E\u0442\r\n\u0432 \u0420\u0443\u0438\u043D\u044B \u0441\u0432\u044F\u0442\u0438\u043B\u0438\u0449\u0430 \u043E\u0445\u043E\u0442\u0438\u0442\u044C\u0441\u044F \u043D\u0430\r\n\u0422\u043E\u0431\u0438-\u041A\u0430\u0434\u0430\u0447\u0438. \u041D\u0435 \u0445\u043E\u0442\u0438\u0442\u0435 \u043F\u043E\u043C\u043E\u0447\u044C?",
        "Target": "\u0412\u044B\u0441\u043B\u0435\u0434\u0438\u0442\u044C \u0422\u043E\u0431\u0438-\u041A\u0430\u0434\u0430\u0447\u0438",
        "Fail": "\u0421\u0447\u0435\u0442\u0447\u0438\u043A \u043D\u0430\u0433\u0440\u0430\u0434\u044B \u0434\u043E\u0445\u043E\u0434\u0438\u0442 \u0434\u043E 0\r\n\u0438\u043B\u0438 \u0438\u0441\u0442\u0435\u043A\u0430\u0435\u0442 \u0432\u0440\u0435\u043C\u044F"
